  height: 100px;
  margin: auto 0;
}
```

To center both horizontally and vertically, combine the two:
```css
.center-both {
  height: 100px;
  margin: auto;
  width: 50%;
}
```
Optionally, you can use absolute positioning and top/left 50% and translate to center:
```css
.center-both {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}
```

